1/ JPMorgan launched JLTXX, the OnChain Liquidity Token Money Market Fund, on May 13.

@jpmorgan seeded the fund with $100m of its own capital. Other launch investors brought day-one TVL to $200m. Seven weeks later, TVL has grown 248% to $695m as of July 3.

@ethereum is currently the only blockchain available for use by investors in the fund.
